data.description: Welcome to the serene haven of Boardwalk Townhomes! Nestled within a gated community established in 2018, this spacious abode offers everything you've been searching for. Step into this inviting tri-level home boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and 2 ½ bathrooms.  On the ground floor, envision the perfect space for a home office, a kids’ playroom, or your own personal workout area, complete with a convenient half bath. Ascend to the expansive second floor, where an open layout seamlessly blends the living room and kitchen, ideal for hosting gatherings. With laminate flooring for hassle-free upkeep, the kitchen dazzles with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting, and shaker cabinets with ample storage space.  Enjoy abundant natural light and a charming balcony, perfect for savoring morning coffee or diving into a good book.  Conveniently located on the second floor, you will find another 1/2 bath with pedestal sink and the laundry room accommodates stackable washer/dryer units. Retreat to the third floor for ultimate privacy, where all bedrooms are situated. The master bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and a master bath featuring a dual sink vanity with quartz countertop. Additional bedrooms offer ample closet space, with a shared bathroom featuring a bathtub/shower combo.  Experience peace of mind knowing the entire home is equipped with a sprinkler system. The garage, with epoxy flooring, comfortably accommodates two cars and offers space for added storage cabinets.  Outside, indulge in community amenities including a pool, spa, and multiple BBQ areas. A children's playground, conveniently located behind the home, ensures easy entertainment for kids and guests alike.  Energy efficiency is ensured with dual pane vinyl windows throughout, along with central air/heat and a tankless water heater. Commuting is a breeze with proximity to the 91 and 15 freeways, while nearby shopping amenities cater to your convenience.  Don't miss the chance to experience this exceptional home firsthand—it's truly a gem waiting to be discovered!
